    filter: "Festive",
    desc: "Azar is a restaurant of oriental and Lebanese specialities located in the heart of Gueliz. It is a place for sharing open to the curious in search of pleasant flavours and captivating culinary discoveries.",
    img: "https://marrakechbestof.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/88EF3142-DE26-422A-BA3F-3465593D385B-700x683.jpeg",
    description: "Azar is a restaurant of oriental and Lebanese specialities located in the heart of Gueliz. It is a place for sharing open to the curious in search of pleasant flavours and captivating culinary discoveries. Delicate aromas of the dishes, generosity of the plates, delicacies on the menu.\nThe restaurant takes care of home deliveries! So, if you prefer to entertain at home for a tête à tête or a last minute party, Azar will deliver everywhere in Marrakech.\nIf you’re a meat lover, try the fillet of beef cooked in the Kanoun, it’s to die for!\n\nIMPORTANT INFORMATION :\n-Payment is done on the spot.\n-Children under 5 years old are not allowed\n-A deposit will be requested by the restaurant for reservations of more than 8 people.\n-From Sunday to Thursday, only one show is scheduled at 9:30 PM\n-On Fridays and Saturdays, two shows are offered: the first at 9:00 PM and the second at 10:00 PM..",
