    tag: "Rooftop",
    filter: "Rooftop",
    desc: "One of the most beautiful terraces in the medina! Located 5 minutes walk from the Jemaa El Fna square, just a stone’s throw from the spice square, is the restaurant L’Mida. The chic and trendy terrace offers a Moroccan fusion menu.",
    img: "https://marrakechbestof.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/5e208d1e6593f798305884-700x700.jpg",
    description: "One of the most beautiful terraces in the medina!\nLocated 5 minutes walk from the Jemaa El Fna square, just a stone’s throw from the spice square, is the restaurant L’Mida.\nThe chic and trendy terrace offers a Moroccan fusion menu. L’Mida is a place where Marrakech traditions and a taste for simple things are mixed.\nAs pleasant to stroll in the sun during the day as to admire the sunset for dinner!\n\nIMPORTANT INFORMATION :\n-A deposit of 100 DH per person will be required by the establishment to confirm the reservation. The deposit will be deducted from the final bill.\n-Use Google map to get there because with all the small streets of the medina, you could get lost.",
