    reviews: 1639,
    tag: "Apéritif",
    filter: "Traditional Moroccan",
    desc: "Wander through the narrow streets of the medina to discover an authentic riad for dinner. The Ksar Essaoussan is a beautiful riad that has kept its assets and authenticity and will welcome you for a traditional Moroccan dinner.",
