    description: "Wander through the narrow streets of the medina to discover an authentic riad for dinner.\nThe Ksar Essaoussan is a beautiful riad that has kept its assets and authenticity and will welcome you for a traditional Moroccan dinner.\nThe restaurant proposes several menus more or less copious from 350 DH (35€) with starter, main course, dessert and aperitifs, drinks and a bottle of wine for 2 persons included!\nYou can also visit the riad and take some pictures on the terrace which gives a breathtaking view of the medina and the Koutoubia, perfect spot for the sunset.\n\nIMPORTANT INFORMATION :\n-Payment is done on the spot.\n-The location is wrong on Google Map. The Ksar Essaoussan is located in the first alley on the left after the M Rooftop, a sign will lead you to the door.",
