    description: "The centerpiece of Riad Nyla, the Spa is a sanctuary dedicated to the senses and well-being. Its skillfully blended colors and finely selected materials will transport you in the space of a moment into an intimate universe.\nPut life in brackets and come enjoy the treatments designed with a team of experts, using local Moroccan products. Scents, aromatics and whispers from the pool envelop the two massage rooms, the treatment room, the sauna and the Hammam.\nThe qualified team of Riad Nyla will accompany you during this immersive experience in the heart of Moroccan tradition.\nOpen to residents, the spa welcomes external visitors by appointment. The latter can extend their experience in the quintessence of relaxation, by passing by the Rooftop, for a detox drink or an invigorating meal.\n\nThe Hammam Marrakchi at Riad Nyla offers a real traditional Moroccan hammam experience with a purifying exfoliation using Kessa gloves and black soap. It also includes a Ghassoul body mask flavored with 7 plants that improves skin purity and elasticity and reduces dryness.\n\nThe treatments are designed with a team of experts, using Nectarome products 100% organic and from the Moroccan soil.\n\nIMPORTANT INFORMATION:\n-Only adults have access to the riad and spa.\n-The spa is closed from 2pm to 3pm for cleaning, please book your packages only between 10am-2pm and 3pm-8pm.\n-The spa is closed on Thursday until 3pm.\n-A staff member will pick you up in front of Dar El Bacha.\n-A staff member will be on site.\n-Booking will be confirmed upon receipt of a 50% deposit.\n-The exchange rate applied is 1 € = 11 DHS.\n\nphoto credit: @lennypellico",
